{"tid":1682551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！休息？","createTime":"2019-10-30T06:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T06:28:43.000Z","uid":320191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a461b0e077f7a494eecbf05ab20456cffbc33fd7","tid":1682551,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"最近熱門一個行動post都冇，反而推哂啲吹水休閒上黎，係香港人開始淡然，已經唔再認真正視活動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n休息左好耐啦，以前有好多活動，商場唱歌又好，遍地開花又好，都係填滿日程表咁濟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今個10月我見到既係大家瘋狂猜測<br />\n地區區議，行動post，策略post全部下沉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Np4QFiA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNp4QFiA.jpg&h=4d24e7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8nnwqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8nnwqg.jpg&h=dcc12ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ReUnwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ReUnwX.jpg&h=ea25e59f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我好想11月2見你地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家幫手落下區貼文宣或者airdrop比其他人share出去<br />\n仲有每晚10點鳩叫幾時真●回歸呀？香港人，係時候再起返身了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地面對緊既係極權丶滿手鮮血既中共，我地更加唔可以因為佢行一步而退一步<br />\n仲記唔記得be water , my friend？香港人反抗？佢地唔單單係口號咁簡單，而係要行動，我地曾經有過200萬位手足一同上街，果時唔係前一日先吹雞行動，至少都有一個星期去號召<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次出post，文筆較差<br />\n但希望大家正視一下問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6352b19b3da6789e588bd3819fb4e1faa1ee7e","tid":1682551,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72854472018f21076cddc492bcbfba5ad62c1a6","tid":1682551,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee738dd2aa3fd3cf703fd6a1dcbb5c3489b4ebff","tid":1682551,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6a37cee38c5fa5af5e69e30b3b0a119700b72d","tid":1682551,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"自推10下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1e5756697503876aea20348f024f09ca478e10","tid":1682551,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"推10下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786b7648fd67a2312ea0ffffd6ac179cf90fb4cd","tid":1682551,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"97959d77545583817aa0f62e83de1fa9f09a2695","tid":1682551,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"b9db7c635dd178fd95f2bbd9a5bc1cc775fa650a","tid":1682551,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f145b4ca99e26ed952bfc3706f49e81e3583240","tid":1682551,"uid":320